   CALIFORNIA SHRUBLANDS AND GRASSLANDS}},
Booktitle = {{23RD TALL TIMBERS FIRE ECOLOGY CONFERENCE: FIRE IN GRASSLAND AND
   SHRUBLAND ECOSYSTEMS}},
